process technology also allowed Micron to reduce the price of the flash drive to 45 cents a gigabyte.&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class="share_submission" style="position:relative;"&gt; &lt;a class="slashpop" href="http://twitter.com/home?status=Micron+Releases+16nm-Process+SSDs+With+Dynamic+Flash+Programming%3A+http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1uErqLB"&gt;&lt;img src="http://a.fsdn.com/sd/twitter_icon_large.png"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="slashpop" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhardware.slashdot.org%2Fstory%2F14%2F09%2F16%2F2030233%2Fmicron-releases-16nm-process-ssds-with-dynamic-flash-programming%3Futm_source%3Dslashdot%26utm_medium%3Dfacebook"&gt;&lt;img src="http://a.fsdn.com/sd/facebook_icon_large.png"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="nobg" href="http://plus.google.com/share?url=http://hardware.slashdot.org/story/14/09/16/2030233/micron-releases-16nm-process-ssds-with-dynamic-flash-programming?utm_source=slashdot&amp;amp;utm_medium=googleplus" onclick="javascript:window.open(this.href,'', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=600,width=600');return false;"&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.gstatic.com/images/icons/gplus-16.png" alt="Share on Google+"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://hardware.slashdot.org/story/14/09/16/2030233/micron-releases-16nm-process-ssds-with-dynamic-flash-programming?utm_source=rss1.0moreanon&amp;amp;utm_medium=feed"&gt;Read more of this story&lt;/a&gt; at Slashdot.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;iframe src="http://slashdot.org/slashdot-it.pl?op=discuss&amp;amp;id=5713493&amp;amp;smallembed=1" style="height: 300px; width: 100%; border: none;"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='http://slashdot.feedsportal.com/c/35028/f/647410/s/3e87aede/sc/4/mf.gif' border='0'/&gt;&lt;br clear='all'/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/206157861137/u/49/f/647410/c/35028/s/3e87aede/sc/4/rc/1/rc.htm" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/206157861137/u/49/f/647410/c/